    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3175120/extras/9d05ceb5f900046ff5a607ebe0e88634.avif?t=1729881949\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3175120/extras_big/9d05ceb5f900046ff5a607ebe0e88634.avif?t=1729881949 width=800 height=432 /></span> Game Features (Demo Version)</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Demo Boss Encounter</strong>: Test your skills against one of the game's challenging bosses, giving you a taste of the high-stakes combat waiting in the full version.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Rewards</strong>: In the demo, you’ll have access to the shop, a mystery box, a slot machine, and a wheel of fortune, offering various ways to spend your gold and test your luck for powerful rewards.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Combat:</strong> Includes a variety of enemies to fight, each requiring quick reflexes and sharp timing.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Side-Scrolling Platforming</strong>: Overcome some of the challenging platforming sections, using wall climbing, jumping, and dashing.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Weapons and Items</strong>: The demo showcases a wide variety of unique weapons and items, each with distinct abilities. Experiment with different combinations to discover powerful synergies and playstyles.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3175120/extras/9f4bcfa340591e68c0a5c2cae21ee830.poster.avif?t=1729881949\" width=800 height=375 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3175120/extras/9f4bcfa340591e68c0a5c2cae21ee830.webm?t=1729881949\"